take the form of a boltzmann - equation in the collisionless regime . to leading order they read \ , , {eq : p1}\ ] ] assuming a spin - independent external harmonic trap . here , is the effective mean - field potential with the spin - dependent coupling constants @xcite , captures the time evolution due to the harmonic trap and the kinetic energy , is the mass of k , and $ ] indicates the commutator in spin space . in the simulations , also higher - order terms of the mean - field interactions are taken
